STATE
v.
William DERBECK. No. 203P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2005. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Peter S. Gilchrist, III, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 15th day of April 2005 by Defendant for Production of Stenographic and Audio Records of Trial Proceedings:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 4th day of May 2005."
